{"tid":1603670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣組]有無諗個整YouTube片 解釋勇武行為","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:33.000Z","uid":94771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf49dd18538203d469cd7dfcc975895362e9f07","tid":1603670,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"話說我老豆藍到紅<br />\n我一直解釋想佢轉黃<br />\n而且佢屌的野 有片解釋比佢睇 佢都唔信<br />\n<br />\n我諗好耐都唔明點解 <br />\n之後有一日發現佢手機Youtube 首頁 我就知點解<br />\n<br />\n另外好多人都對評論當收音機聽,用Youtube解釋勇武行為 文宣成效高好多<br />\n解釋的重點  <strong>爆站 放火 師鳥</strong>原因<br />\n放映會可用 而且 介紹比上一輩睇 解釋比佢地聽所有行為都係有原因<br />\n唔係無謂發洩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b895c7a017deb9e8197ec463de91640b97f28b9f","tid":1603670,"uid":74190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n成個連登 九成黑警post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6904924789dc91162576e3d417175a9c62356752","tid":1603670,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da9d93814fdb2e8c8624fdc87c908c272c33d33","tid":1603670,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"Check this:<br />\nHKGETV: 勇武最強文宣片現已流出，大家一齊了解背後精神同理念<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593088</a><br />\n<br />\n請善用搜尋功能"},{"pid":"20dc7b5c936298235ba61c9cd5f3b9f85360b2ca","tid":1603670,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"And